title: That Metal Show S13E02 Living Colour, Sevendust.mkv
description: Hosts Eddie, Don and Jim welcome Living Colour's Corey Glover and Vernon Reid to the show for the first time and discuss the span of their career from opening for the Rolling Stones to new music. Sevendust drummer Morgan Rose talks about his latest projects and Manowar's Joey DeMaio joins on the Metal Modem. Joel Hoekstra brings classical edge as guest guitarist.
